最好戴返respirator。亦唔好為你習慣左而開心。<br />\n<br />\n肺係內臟有自己function，手係出面做粗重野，內傷同外傷係有重要的分別的。"},{"pid":"19228b059424c3c83c446bd565e8dfc24914d090","tid":1374961,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21c937a0ba8977883e8f54394faabc9131c1a26","tid":1374961,"uid":6848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9rYSZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9rYSZK.png&h=37948fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前線應該應該個個都要有盔有罩有filter有gear<br />\n<br />\n建議配搭<br />\n6200 半面罩 加密封既潛水鏡<br />\n6800 全面罩 痴反光紙或有遮掩既頭盔 (如上圖右邊)<br />\n基本催淚配備 6006 filter<br />\n升級少少 +P100 要配502轉接<br />\n再高級啲 +7093 要配502轉接<br />\n超級神裝 60926"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"反光紙係玻璃紙定膠紙"},{"pid":"102bb6f640eac0ed6520ef0d40df62960df114eb","tid":1374961,"uid":104287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:11:29.000Z","msg":"gm31 有冇得諗<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOkVVj0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOkVVj0.png&h=0c3d90f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c92cdc2b5c8114d2b19a86d91e89cadea5771787","tid":1374961,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:12:23.000Z","msg":"r95 係咪ok?"},{"pid":"54e2a8480969a91389be452fb4190c89b2e2ebff","tid":1374961,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"防炒辣蟹果d豬嘴幾錢個"},{"pid":"4d4fcf6a67aaf006502b961d1e56401460ed10b2","tid":1374961,"uid":6848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19228b059424c3c83c446bd565e8dfc24914d090","tid":1374961,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21c937a0ba8977883e8f54394faabc9131c1a26","tid":1374961,"uid":6848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9rYSZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9r